  "texts": [
    "Therefore, G-Eval was adopted for evaluating the NLG processes in this experiment, with the high-performance LLM, gpt-4o-2024-05-13, used as the evaluation LLM.",
    "In G-Eval, evaluation criteria are provided as natural language descriptions, and for each NLG input-output pair, a score between 0 and 1 is generated based on how well the pair aligns with the criteria.",
    "Additionally, G-Eval outputs a logical explanation of the reasoning behind each score.",
    "In this experiment, the author verified that all evaluation explanations were coherent and acceptable to human readers, ensuring the validity of the evaluation criteria, process, and results.In Experiment 1, we assessed the generation of service names that capture the key points of the statements.",
    "The evaluation metric provided to G-Eval was: \"Evaluate the extracted service names from the user's statements."
  ],
